<p>It is full of rock-solid and high quality information  for those  beginning their model train collecting.</p>
<p>Even modelers with vast experience will gain much insight as there is  an unbelievable amount of useful  information in this ebook . It always  helps to have something that brings you back to all of the basics and  can provide a reference for use on a daily basis.</p>
<p>In spite of all the research I have done,   I still found more than a  few tips in <strong><a rel="nofollow" href="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/beginner" target="_blank">Model  Trains for Beginners</a></strong> that could have saved  me hundreds of  dollars had I been aware of them before. Further, this information is  for all scales, not just <a href="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/trains-o-scale/home/" >trains O scale</a> model trains.</p>
<p>It covers the essential basics from the  ground up including the  language of model trains, how to conceptualize your plan, and the design  and creation of fantastic layouts that are easy to run and problem  free. You will also get exposure to advanced realism techniques like  weathering, how to make your layout look  dated, as well as controllers  and tips for those people who are not  Electricians, and so much more.</p>
<p>This is a very well priced ebook at $47, as you  would not normally find this amount of condensed, straight to the point  information in one  book, and comes with $135 in free bonuses. Again, it would be necessary to purchase 5 or 6 books to get the equivalent amount of information.</p>
<p>It also comes with 7 bonuses that make the  investment well worth it.</p>
