      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img style="margin-right:20px" src="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/wp-content/uploads/Girder Bridge_24.jpg" alt="Girder Bridge" border="0" align="left" /><br />
<b>does any one here remember the name of this construction set from the 60&#8242;s?</b><br />
<script type="text/javascript">
