      <description><![CDATA[The Cass Scenic Railroad I &#160; Morning mist, like a transparent sheath, rose from the green-carpeted Cheat Mountain in West Virginia&#8217;s Monongahela National Forest on that Memorial Day weekend, but the hot sun quickly intercepted it during its gentle ascent, leaving a flawlessly blue sky. Like a pocket of history, somehow frozen in time, the [...]<p><a href="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/accessories-2/chesapeake-ohio/">Chesapeake Ohio</a> is a post from: <a href="http://trainsoscaledepot.com">Trains O Scale</a>:blog where you can get news on Trains O Scale and other model train collecting news.</p>
