      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img style="margin-right:20px" src="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/wp-content/uploads/Gondola Load_16.jpg" alt="Gondola Load" border="0" align="left" /></p>
<h2>Top 5 Vacation Destinations – Lets Vacation Round The World</h2>
<p>When having a vacation, people usually have a dilemma where to go.&nbsp; As a guide, here are the top 5 vacation destinations around the world:</p>
<p>(1)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;New York City is simply a tourist and vacationer haven.&nbsp; People flock to the iconic Times Square to stare at the most outlandish strip of flashy neon signs which attract a little more than 35 million tourists a year. Whether it is to watch a Broadway show, rummage the stores for a shopping spree, or and tour the museums like the Metropolitan, the city that never sleeps is a sure tourist hit. Don&rsquo;t forget to have a hot dog!</p>
<p>(2)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Las Vegas offers a lot more than just a gambler&rsquo;s paradise.&nbsp; Neon lights, risqu&eacute; entertainment, and casinos make Las Vegas a sure vacationer&rsquo;s destination.&nbsp; The nightlife sizzles and the daytime can be for loads shopping from you previous night&rsquo;s winnings! &nbsp;</p>
<p>(3)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;The beaches of Cozumel, the colonial cities, the Aztec pyramids, and the glorious food make Mexico for everyone. Mariachis, tacos, and endless white sand stretches are just some reasons why Mexico is a dream vacation destination.</p>
<p>(4)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;White sand, pretty corals, warm people, sunny days ahead &ndash; what is not to like about the Caribbean?&nbsp; The whole chain of Caribbean islands promises the tourist not just loads of sun, but loads of fun, too.</p>
<p>(5)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;In Italy, you are entitled to a lot of choices.&nbsp; Take a ride on a Vespa or a gondola, have your fill or pasta or gelato, hike through the fields of Tuscany or the mountains of the Italian Alps.&nbsp; Whatever your choice will be, the gastronomic and visual wonders are endless.</p>
<p><strong>About the Author</strong><br />
