      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img style="margin-right:20px" src="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/wp-content/uploads/Double Track_4.jpg" alt="Double Track" border="0" align="left" /></p>
<h2>Tracking Pay Per Click</h2>
<p>Tracking pay per click advertising is one concept that people tend to forget.&nbsp; It is essential that you are targeting your potential market with a high search volume and low search results.&nbsp; When tracking your advertising campaigns, you must know what your competitors are using, what their strategies are and how to overpower them.</p>
<p>With all the competition in pay per click advertising, it is difficult for a small business to get on top of the search results.&nbsp; In fact, some advertisers are paying over $10 just for one click and most cannot compete.&nbsp; There is a solution, understanding what keywords your competitors are using and learning from their techniques.</p>
<p>Keywordspy.com is a tool that can be used to see what specific keywords companies are using to drive traffic to their site.&nbsp; It is essential that you use this to your advantage.&nbsp; Pick keywords that are different than top pay per click advertisers but very similar.&nbsp; Adding one word to a keyword can dramatically change your ranking in the search results. Also, finding how much your cost per click must be in order to compete can impact your campaign strategy.</p>
<p>In order to track your pay per click advertising, you must be willing to search your keywords on a daily basis.&nbsp; This will consistently show you where you are placed on the search results.&nbsp; Relying solely on Google, will lead to poor click through rates and very little profit.&nbsp; Also, testing your links is a must when starting a new campaign.&nbsp; Companies have found this out the hard way after spending thousands of dollars driving their customers to an unknown Web address.</p>
<p>Learning how to master pay per click advertising is a skill that involves years of patience and practice. In order to gain a full advantage over your competitors, Double Digit CTR will show you the successful techniques and tactics to start increasing your click through rates.&nbsp; Learning on your own will take time, but for $39.99, you can speed up the process to drive more customers to your site now. Double Digit CTR is packed with 9 videos, a cheat sheet, keyword tool, Mp3&rsquo;s, and a niche research report.&nbsp; All the information you need to find valuable keywords, spying techniques, and successful landing pages are all in this system.&nbsp; If you use Double Digit CTR&rsquo;s proven techniques correctly, it is assured that your company will be seen by millions of people.</p>
