      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img style="margin-right:20px" src="http://trainsoscaledepot.com/wp-content/uploads/Gal Tank_23.jpg" alt="Gal Tank" border="0" align="left" /><br />
<b>What fish could be put in a 10 Gal tank?</b><br />
<script type="text/javascript">
ch_client = "mdcson";
ch_width = 468;
ch_height = 250;
ch_type = "mpu";
ch_sid = "Trains O Scale";
ch_backfill = 1;
