<p></i></p>
<p>Aww &#8211; I love that film!  It&#8217;s called &#8220;A Little Romance&#8221;.  It started off in Paris.  The boy and the girl ran away to Venice and to kiss under the Bridge of Sighs at sunset.  </p>
<p>The little girl was Diane Lane when she was 13 or 14 years old and it was her first film. I still have it in VHS.</p>
