<p>3- Anthony H. Cordesman and Arleigh A. Burke, &ldquo;The Gulf and Transition: Executive Summary and Major Policy Recommendations&rdquo; (October 30, 2000). </p>
<p>4- Anthony H. Cordesman and Arleigh A. Burke, &ldquo;The US Military and the Evolving Challenges in the Middle East&rdquo; (March 9, 2002), 3. </p>
<p>5- Anthony H. Cordesman and Arleigh A. Burke, &ldquo;The US Military and the Evolving Challenges in the Middle East&rdquo; (March 9, 2002), 3. </p>
<p>6- Anthony H. Cordesman and Arleigh A. Burke, &ldquo;The US Military and the Evolving Challenges in the Middle East&rdquo; (March 9, 2002), 4. </p>
